0. german national animal seems cool
============================
The national animal of Germany is the eagle (specifically the Bundesadler or Federal Eagle), which is stylized as a black, one-headed eagle with red claws and beak. It is almost always drawn in a heraldic, upright position facing towards its right (the viewer's left) with wings displayed and feathers stylized. 
